    "description": "<p>This skill is only effective while you are equipped with a [Two-Handed] weapon.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>You gain a + [POW Mod] bonus to the damage roll done on a Round where you declared [Standby].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(SR 2): When you are in the [Standby] state you also gain + 1 to your [Defense Checks].</p>\n<p>(SR 3): You can immediately reduce [Hate] by - 1 when you declare [Standby].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A fighting style that focuses on powerful blows with large weapons. The power of the blow that is released after accumulating power is unrivaled.</p>",
